{"tid":1856312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人就黎飲撚哂紐西蘭d水","createTime":"2020-02-01T14:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T05:30:44.000Z","uid":273901,"like":432,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":138,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0909ec6319d7bdf0ff849bb3bb42cd37a6da1d","tid":1856312,"uid":273901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:23:37.000Z","msg":"//我先從下面這張圖開始談起，近年來在紐西蘭大量取水的中資瓶裝水公司引起紐西蘭人的關注，並試圖對政府施壓，要求政府禁止將紐西蘭水裝瓶外銷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HsLxSO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsLxSO5.jpg&h=cfcda816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個叫做Wake up NZ的自媒體1/17發這個圖，要求大家重視中國不停汲取紐西蘭水源這個議題。<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/XXzvoa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FXXzvoa&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=fa7b42d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/XXzvoa</a><br />\n這張圖被狂轉發了近4200多次，而我們台灣也被列在上面，跟著中國的形象一起廣傳。<br />\n如果你覺得不爽，那要求紐西蘭政府跟台灣建立外交關係這個請願你一定要連署！<br />\n<strong><ins>這是一位叫做Edd Forrest的紐西蘭人，在國會請願網頁上創立了一個連署，要求國會敦促紐西蘭政府<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">承認台灣</span>並與台灣建立外交關係。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫台灣，現在馬上連署去：<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/drYd0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FdrYd0k&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=2f6d58d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/drYd0k</a> <br />\n在2/3截止!</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">幫幫台灣，現在馬上連署去：<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/drYd0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FdrYd0k&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=2f6d58d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/drYd0k</a> <br />\n在2/3截止!</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫幫台灣，現在馬上連署去：<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/drYd0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FdrYd0k&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=2f6d58d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/drYd0k</a> <br />\n在2/3截止!</span><br />\n<br />\n只要填入姓、名跟email就完成！<br />\n而且依據紐西蘭規定，#不限紐西蘭籍都可以請願）<br />\n<br />\n#目前這個連署只剩下一天，在2/3截止。雖然紐西蘭國會請願並沒有一定的門檻，但是 #現在總共<span style=\"color: orange;\">只有182個人連署 ，實在不太好看</span><br />\n我不知道剩下一天究竟能夠找到多少人一起，但我真的很希望看到在一天之內，這個連署人數能夠向上衝到讓紐西蘭政府和民眾覺得這是一件重要的事情。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">連署去：<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/drYd0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FdrYd0k&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXtzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=2f6d58d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/drYd0k</a> (連署只剩下一天！)</span>"},{"pid":"bc2032f0283e7cc78db756f6c72665bdf2289fe7","tid":1856312,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5451c62592004b4a22c75143d5fc852b432edd8b","tid":1856312,"uid":3776,"like":330,"dislike":1,"score":329,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:29:12.000Z","msg":"bu你阿嬤 我地比錢飲屎水<br />\n你班大陸哩食紐西蘭水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9478d1e89540341b181b9decc267616e1a32cfd4","tid":1856312,"uid":123848,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"可以加價了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8690a8f32b04b12f31518e5f9745785d5ce3b1e9","tid":1856312,"uid":326725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:42:45.000Z","msg":"全部簽曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c227328afb0bae80e6e81632ab47d3c5318237","tid":1856312,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5451c62592004b4a22c75143d5fc852b432edd8b","tid":1856312,"uid":3776,"like":330,"dislike":1,"score":329,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:29:12